Dynamic music legends and frequent collaborators Keith Jarrett, Gary Peacock and Jack DeJohnette combine their talents for this rich, melodic performance recorded live in Tokyo at the Hitomi Memorial Hall. A number of beloved standards come to life as never before in this celebration of the past century&#039;s greatest musical accomplishments.
